{"title":"瑞雪（图片）","authors":["唐力","晓黎"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐力摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓黎配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是小鸭白色的湖水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是母鸡白色的草丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是孩子们白色的欢乐国度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是来年金色的收获宣言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们到哪里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们带走了往日的调皮和喧闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庭院外，一定有许许多多故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光似乎把嬉笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透进栅栏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听得见雪花嗞嗞的融化声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听得见冬眠的草儿轻轻地打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院寂寂，成为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于我们的世界——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸭子悠悠地模仿划水，以待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年春江水暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母鸡们呢，贴着柔柔的雪晒太"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恢复疲惫，什么也不想也同样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐趣无限"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}